&lt;p>&lt;em>A four mile walk of mostly level terrain including the famous Kitty Jay&amp;rsquo;s Grave, Bowerman&amp;rsquo;s Nose, Swallerton Gate, a Logan Stone, Ladder Stile and many more&lt;/em>&lt;/p>
